|WKB                          QUEST REWARDS
|CKB=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=

|YKOWhen you complete all objectives for a quest, your rewards are
granted automatically. You do not need to turn anything in or
visit a specific NPC - the system handles it for you.

|WKBReward Types:|XX0

  |YKBExperience |YKO- Bonus experience points added directly to your
  total. The amount is shown by the waysteward before acceptance.

  |YKBGold |YKO- Coins deposited into your inventory. The amount is
  shown in the waysteward's quest dialogue.

  |YKBQuest Points |YKO- Permanent quest progress points used by the
  wider level progression system. The amount is shown before acceptance.

  |YKBItems |YKO- Some quests grant special objects as rewards. These
  are placed in your inventory when the quest completes.

|WKBDifficulty and Rewards:|XX0

  |YKOHigher-level quests with tougher objectives tend to offer better
  rewards. The waysteward dialogue shows the suggested level range
  relative to your level:

    |gKB  green   |YKO- Well below your level. Easy, smaller rewards.
    |GKB  GREEN   |YKO- At or near your level. Moderate challenge.
    |YKB  YELLOW  |YKO- Slightly above your level. Good rewards.
    |RKB  RED     |YKO- Significantly above your level. Great rewards,
                   but dangerous.

|WKBCompletion:|XX0

  |YKOEach quest can only be completed once. Completed quests are
  tracked permanently on your character. Use |YKBmyquests |YKOto see
  which quests you have finished.

|CKB=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=
